    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>
      MedCart Kenya was founded with a simple yet powerful vision: to make healthcare accessible to every Kenyan, no matter where they are. We recognized that many people across the country face challenges accessing quality medicines and health products, whether due to distance, availability, or affordability.
    </p>
    <p>
      As a licensed online pharmacy, we bridge the gap between patients and the healthcare products they need. We deliver genuine, high-quality medicines, supplements, personal care products, and medical devices right to your doorstep, serving communities across Kenya with reliability and care.
    </p>

